  "judgment": {
    "summary": "The user explores the nuances of \"fake news,\" questioning whether it is a legitimate phenomenon or merely a rhetorical weapon used to dismiss unfavorable reporting. The assistant responds by distinguishing between intentional disinformation (fabricated lies) and biased reporting (framing/selection), maintaining a descriptive and analytical tone throughout the conversation.",
